    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Dec 27, 2016</title>
      <link>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-27/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Dec 2016 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-27/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Using big data for security only provides insight, not protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The technology is here now, already deployed, already catching criminals stealing sensitive data and delivering early alerts on data breaches and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cio.com.au/article/612032/using-big-data-security-only-provides-insight-protection/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cio.com.au/article/612032/using-big-data-security-only-provides-insight-protection/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR) Market Research Report Now Available&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Republic of East Vancouver Research Corridor has published a new research study titled Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR) Market  Growth, Share, Opportunities, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.republic-news.org/news/endpoint-detection-response-edr-market-research-report-now-available-research-corridor/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.republic-news.org/news/endpoint-detection-response-edr-market-research-report-now-available-research-corridor/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Year in Review: Top tech stories of 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was a big year for tech companies in North Texas  and for the perception of DFW as a tech hub. Several studies showed the area is rapidly adding &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2016/12/27/year-in-review-top-tech-stories-of-2016.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2016/12/27/year-in-review-top-tech-stories-of-2016.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Palo Alto Networks Inc (PANW) Files Form 4 Insider Selling : Steffan&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Market Digest The Company&amp;rsquo;s security platform consists of three elements: its Next-Generation Firewall its Advanced Endpoint Protection and its Threat Intelligence &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.themarketdigest.org/201612/palo-alto-networks-inc-panw-files-form-4-insider-selling-steffan-tomlinson-sells-2332-shares-3/3220014/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.themarketdigest.org/201612/palo-alto-networks-inc-panw-files-form-4-insider-selling-steffan-tomlinson-sells-2332-shares-3/3220014/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;We run down the worst security breaches of 2016 and reveal how to stay safe&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wired.co.uk This year, Yahoo disclosed two data breaches of its service, the first contained 500 million user accounts and happened in 2014; the second involved &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.wired.co.uk/article/biggest-hacks-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.wired.co.uk/article/biggest-hacks-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Opinion/Editorial: Scanning of licenses needs limits&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a world where privacy has been so eroded that massive data breaches now make us shrug instead of shudder  unless we&amp;rsquo;re directly a victim &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dailyprogress.com/opinion/opinion-editorial-scanning-of-licenses-needs-limits/article_10508b96-cc41-11e6-bc1e-d70abb0c84e1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.dailyprogress.com/opinion/opinion-editorial-scanning-of-licenses-needs-limits/article_10508b96-cc41-11e6-bc1e-d70abb0c84e1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Top 10 Most Significant Data Breaches in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;news, advisory and Mac OS X tips and tricks to keep your Mac safe and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://mackeeper.com/blog/post/313-mackeeper-top-10-most-significant-data-breaches-in-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://mackeeper.com/blog/post/313-mackeeper-top-10-most-significant-data-breaches-in-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Haiyan Song: Organizations will Integrate Machine Learning Tech to Automate&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ExecutiveBiz (blog) User behavioral analytics-based technologies will also support strategies against data breaches and offer real-time insights on who has access to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2016/12/haiyan-song-organizations-will-integrate-machine-learning-tech-to-automate-data-breach-response/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://blog.executivebiz.com/2016/12/haiyan-song-organizations-will-integrate-machine-learning-tech-to-automate-data-breach-response/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s Data Breaches Unlikely to Derail Verizon Deal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hundreds of U.S. companies fall prey to hackers every year and, in many cases, the data breaches neither hurt bottom lines nor scare away customers &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-12-27/yahoo-s-data-breaches-seen-unlikely-to-derail-verizon-deal&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-12-27/yahoo-s-data-breaches-seen-unlikely-to-derail-verizon-deal&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Security breach us bank credit cards&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MasterCard or. Aug 28, 2014 . Two of the nation&amp;rsquo;s 10 biggest banks &amp;ndash; U.S. Bank and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://worldinprayer.org/nuin/wiv&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://worldinprayer.org/nuin/wiv&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon Likely to Complete Yahoo Buy Despite Hacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Inc. (YHOO) may have disclosed two massive data breaches potentially impacting millions of consumers, but it&amp;rsquo;s not likely to be enough to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.investopedia.com/news/verizon-likely-complete-yahoo-buy-despite-hacks/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.investopedia.com/news/verizon-likely-complete-yahoo-buy-despite-hacks/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;80% of complaints about spam involve online gambling, loans&lt;/h3&gt;
